name: minnesota-school-district-boundaries-school-year-2003-2004
notes: This file represents the boundaries of all public school districts in the state of Minnesota for school year 2003-2004. Minnesota school districts identify their current elementary, middle and high school attendance area boundaries on a yearly basis using large format maps supplied by the Land Management Information Center (LMIC). This file is maintained at LMIC but is also supplied to the State of Minnesota Legislative Coordinating Commission GIS Office. The LCC keeps the 'official' school distirct information for the State of Minnesota. This school district file was dissolved from a file containing both the school district and attendance boundaries to produce just school district boundaries.
